{"tid":1468260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"割啦屌你老母","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:14:07.000Z","uid":55958,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f82a24ddaca53e68ccdfc66ccb58dc3e09e9a5c3","tid":1468260,"uid":55958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:11:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">割你老母呀！<br />\n我呢Ｄ淆底獸，就係唔敢上前線<br />\n前線冇我地呢Ｄ後排咁多時間係後面慢慢諗點做<br />\n前線就係要即刻處理所有突發事<br />\n前線就係要冒住更大既風險比人拉同打<br />\n我地睇既係直播，人地企既係現場<br />\n話要割果Ｄ人，去前線一日感受下先<br />\n返黎都要割既，我割埋你老母呀！</span>"},{"pid":"e717409789bde65c48c5982be7e3b23fa2bc0b43","tid":1468260,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:11:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1FNfTAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1FNfTAU.jpg&h=7becab2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E9TyFfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE9TyFfU.jpg&h=0b41b5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8shGO9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8shGO9f.jpg&h=e0856b12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"013f157a5f112feee6426760b35d72d9a637843c","tid":1468260,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:12:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2e166b46db3dfa91c1326112f446afc8194fcb","tid":1468260,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:12:27.000Z","msg":"【跪求大家入黎睇下，我好想香港贏】關於鬼關於衝動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1466732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1466732</a>"},{"pid":"5f146cbb33c2a0d90da2df2ab1a5df303b720cd8","tid":1468260,"uid":205734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:12:52.000Z","msg":"玩分化死撚開"},{"pid":"9eeaa584a3370aa80bcdb263fefa9e043e35b3e8","tid":1468260,"uid":49202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:13:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c94382fbf7d86f99921f2ec55185c3c8d03b343","tid":1468260,"uid":292067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:13:46.000Z","msg":"何妖實恥笑<br />\n我由頭到尾無割過 無被割 無被指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地班撚樣 少少野都割又分化互屌互指責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n---------<br />\n記住 反對/屌人時 比埋建議 咁就<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\